regen.absent_element: specification for handling errors during import from files or copying data from existing structures
regen.new_specification: The system shall handle and notify users of any errors that occur during the creation of a new structure by importing from a file or copying data from an existing structure.

regen.absent_element: error handling for invalid or unsupported file types during import
regen.new_specification: The system shall handle and notify the user of errors when attempting to import from an invalid or unsupported file type.

regen.absent_element: notification or confirmation after global renumbering of bridge keys
regen.new_specification: The system shall notify or confirm with the user after a global renumbering of bridge keys has been successfully completed.

label: The renumbering shall be restricted depending on the user privilege
absence: The renumbering function shall be restricted depending on the user privilege
